e warriors have one EB weapon and I rarely see them lose aggro.  Seems to me that it would benefit you more to have an EB weap in one hand, and say a Render of Souls(all around nice weap) in the offhand.  Just food for thought.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->[65 Overlord]<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=132589">Veteran Kilzalot Drachonis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
